{"tid":2414144,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"醫管局：不認同醫護發布「安心出行」失實資訊 籲免誤導市民","createTime":"2021-02-19T07:57:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T15:32:46.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fc10674bf40113febf3738c70e05ffc2385383f5","tid":2414144,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T07:57:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/isxd_WxqQMOnUKvskv6lTA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzOS42OTkyNDgxMjAzMDA4/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/wxDKKPpZ0gL5HaY9lkkMwA--~B/aD03MDk7dz0xMDY0O2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/singtao.com.hk/1cef105c125e43e3a4d0d9421a6cf744\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fisxd_WxqQMOnUKvskv6lTA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzOS42OTkyNDgxMjAzMDA4%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FwxDKKPpZ0gL5HaY9lkkMwA--~B%2FaD03MDk7dz0xMDY0O2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fsingtao.com.hk%2F1cef105c125e43e3a4d0d9421a6cf744&h=c4252912&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】醫院管理局發言人重申，絕不認同部分醫護人員發布「安心出行」應用程式的失實資訊。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局就部分醫護人員發布「安心出行」應用程式的失實資訊發聲明，指局方作為公共醫療機構，一直鼓勵市民在不同層面同心抗疫。防止病毒傳播及追蹤確診病人的接觸者，是抗疫工作中的重要環節，醫管局一直切實執行相關措施，亦鼓勵市民、病人及醫護人員作出配合。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局相信，在保障私隱的大前提下，市民透過「安心出行」應用程式自行記錄出入公共場所的資料，有助防止病毒傳播及進行接觸追蹤，市民亦可透過有關記錄得知相關風險。醫管局絕不認同部分醫護人員發布「安心出行」應用程式的失實資訊，呼籲有關醫護人員停止發布有關資訊，以免誤導市民。"},{"pid":"c451998067c6bcb7a414dfd5a368bba5ef3eaec7","tid":2414144,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T07:58:04.000Z","msg":"醫護講咗乜嘢<br />\n<br />\n醫管局班仆街咁大反應?"},{"pid":"6a6b432eecbbd3d4e77c3f37a8ae135ca3ae2827","tid":2414144,"uid":26385,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c451998067c6bcb7a414dfd5a368bba5ef3eaec7","tid":2414144,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T07:58:04.000Z","msg":"醫護講咗乜嘢<br />\n<br />\n醫管局班仆街咁大反應?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T07:59:11.000Z","msg":"乜都無講<br />\n打稻草人啫<br />\n即係醫護係政府下一個玩具<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"867f058169271e6493d7e9ddea6dd9d4c29b4c7c","tid":2414144,"uid":178875,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T08:00:23.000Z","msg":"佢唔講我都唔知班醫護講左乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過醫管局反對得咁就一定係班醫護做左啱的野了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48f8bbc6f7862b47ca68a70773ea03fd9e578453","tid":2414144,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T08:00:26.000Z","msg":"又要洗幾億請律師搞鳩醫護<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0d632950bfa3751fed0837b2db31eac452baff4","tid":2414144,"uid":78039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c451998067c6bcb7a414dfd5a368bba5ef3eaec7","tid":2414144,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T07:58:04.000Z","msg":"醫護講咗乜嘢<br />\n<br />\n醫管局班仆街咁大反應?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T08:01:17.000Z","msg":"搞掂咗司法同公務員同港台，醫護邊會無份"},{"pid":"be3ce60817a7b177acf8dfcdf2519a2977daff7c","tid":2414144,"uid":86828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T08:01:32.000Z","msg":"寫標題嗰個係咪唔識中文 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21b438d7d91e923e09b1642eca585fd05ad4d1fb","tid":2414144,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"867f058169271e6493d7e9ddea6dd9d4c29b4c7c","tid":2414144,"uid":178875,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T08:00:23.000Z","msg":"佢唔講我都唔知班醫護講左乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過醫管局反對得咁就一定係班醫護做左啱的野了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}